Package: BSTFA
Title: Bayesian Spatio-Temporal Factor Analysis Model
Description: This package implements Bayesian spatio-temporal factor analysis models for analyzing multivariate data observed over space and time. It provides tools for model fitting, spatial and temporal interpolation, and visualization of latent factors and loadings to support inference and exploration of spatio-temporal behavior.
Version: 0.1.0
